Sensational popstar Davido visited Port Harcourt recently but not to thrill fans with his performance. David Adeleke aka Davido visited Portharcourt to partner with the Rivers State Government to groom new music talents. He visited the Governor at the government house and expressed his resolve to grow music talents outside Lagos and empower young people through music. In addition, he is planning a concert which local and international artists will perform to bring more exposure to the upcoming talents. Governor Wike and Davido. Nigerian News update This is an indication that Davido is not just a musician but is gearing towards being a mentor and a voice for young people. That is how some politicians start in certain societies.